00:22:44.029 --> 00:22:46.407
Araw-araw kong binabasa
ang orihinal na draft ng aking ina.

00:22:46.490 --> 00:22:47.658
Nagtataka tuloy ako

00:22:48.409 --> 00:22:49.994
